-----------------------------------------------------------------------
                               @{b}New in 2.39@{ub}
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

 @{b}New in 2.0@{ub}

 @{b}1)@{ub} Much more compact and user-friendly MUI preferences

 @{b}2)@{ub} Memory usage now drastically reduced! (was almost 1Mb)

 @{b}3)@{ub} File size slashed from almost 300K to 30K!!!

 @{b}4)@{ub} FileID.library usage now version independant

 @{b}5)@{ub} New CLI option, so you can use Zoom as a default tool

 @{b}6)@{ub} Extra OS 3.5 functionality



 @{b}New in 2.39@{ub}

 @{b}1)@{ub} Locale support added

 @{b}2)@{ub} Bug fixes to CLI wildcard handling

 @{b}3)@{ub} False IO error reports fixed

 @{b}4)@{ub} File size up to 60K, not exactly a feature :-( 
